      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to satisfy the most discerning collector. Every surface reflects a commitment to excellence, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior. Mechanically superior and visually striking, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends standard pre-owned expectations. We invite you to experience the pinnacle of automotive preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
