    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather is supple and unmarked, and every button and switch retains its tactile, factory-new feel. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service history and performing with absolute precision and smoothness. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a pristine, investment-grade example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
