    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of this car, and it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition, inside and out\u2014seriously, it's flawless! I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it as much as I have. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for your next adventure. Shoot me a message if you want to take a look!",
